    About this hotel

    Set beside the Jambil Khwar River, this relaxed hotel is an 8-minute walk from the Swat Museum, 14 minutes away by foot from the Butkara I archaeological site and 6 km from Saidu Sharif Airport. …

    Modest, air-conditioned rooms feature Wi-Fi, satellite TV and minifridges. Some rooms have balconies.

    There's a warmly decorated restaurant and a conference hall. Breakfast and afternoon tea are also available.
